<h2>River Description</h2>
<p>
Paddling Time: 3-4 days<br>
Portages: Many! Rock climbing skills (and hardware) useful.<br>
<br>
<b>Put In:</b> Lion Campground, 5 miles east of Hwy.33 on FS Road 6N31. (Elev: 2980')&nbsp;
<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=34.5582,+-%20119.1603+%28Put-in%29&amp;hl=en&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;z=17&amp;ll=34.5582,-%20119.1603&amp;spn=0.00376,0.010632&amp;t=h&amp;om=1">
google map</a><br>
&nbsp;
</p>
<p>
<b>Take Out:</b> Shiell's Park at Old Telegraph Rd Bridge, in Fillmore (Elev: 400')&nbsp;
<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=34.40405936,+-%20118.9304+%28Take-out%29&amp;hl=en&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;z=17&amp;ll=34.40405936,-%20118.9304&amp;spn=0.00376,0.010632&amp;t=h&amp;om=1">
google map</a><br>
&nbsp;
</p>
<p>
<b>Shuttle:</b> 45 miles, 1.25 hours<br>
<br>
Average Gradient: 82 fpm
</p>
